snippet.title: Checkmate Showdown | Meet the Bishop
snippet.description:
The Bishop is the rushdown of the game: He hits hard and fast but has very few defensive tools.

Thanks to his speed and his many approach mix-ups, the Bishop excels in keeping the pressure on his opponent whether in the air or on the ground.
Once the guard has passed, the bishop can do what he does best: A series of combos throwing the opponent in all directions.

If you like fast characters that specialize in close range combat, The Bishop is who you want to main.
